  "keyFeatures": [
    "Instant movie and TV show search via TMDB with built-in fallback",
    "Plugin-based scraper system using encrypted .rink files",
    "Custom HTML5 and Vidstack video player with HLS/M3U8 support",
    "Range-request proxy for streaming with M3U8 rewriting",
    "16-language i18n support",
    "Fully configurable via environment variables at runtime",
    "Docker, Vercel, Railway, Render, and Cloudflare Workers deployment",
    "Optional PostgreSQL or JSON-file database",
    "Optional authentication with local login",
    "Local media library support via File System Access API",
    "Animated background shaders (falling dither, neon dither)",
    "shiopa CLI for cloning, configuring, and managing scraper sources",
    "Dark/light theme with accent hue picker"
  ],
